# This file is just a reference template.
# The actual .env file is auto-generated by the app the first time
# you enter your API key in the Setup screen — you do NOT need to
# edit this manually.
#
# If you prefer to set it up yourself before running the app,
# copy this file to ".env" and paste your key:
#
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_key_here
#
# Get a free key at: https://console.groq.com/keys
